{"tid":1541053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼]暴徒攬炒，香港永不超生？咪on9啦","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:17:22.000Z","uid":12792,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a377fc19ce1e026681cdd596117a030b3a2c7b07","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"[轉貼]<br />\n<br />\n近日，聽到好幾位淺黃朋友傾開，點解後生仔要搞破壞，而不每星期和平示威表達訴求<br />\n唔評論和平示威能否達到目的，因為各執一詞。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後生仔搞破壞會影響民生同香港永遠玩完？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n影響民生我同意，但要分清楚，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">激進示威活動只屬事件性，屬於短暫性/一次性</span></span>。外國咁多暴動(真係死人)，例泰國曼谷，法國巴黎等等，佢地經濟有冇受到永久性影響？好明顯完全冇！<br />\n做生意嘅人好明白呢d只係短暫性影響，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會影響社會結構同營商環境。</span></span><br />\n短時間社會經濟會受影響，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">絕對可以慢慢修復！</span></span><br />\n再者，如果一個社會人民可以表達訴求同爭取，如果我係生意佬(純粹個人睇法)，我會非常欣賞同覺得呢度好值得投資，因為我唔需要下下睇政府面色(你估佢哋入中國做生意，用咗幾多資源同啲官打關係？)<br />\n<br />\n反而<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果容許政府專橫、執法者濫權、選擇性執法、司法不獨立等等，呢啲先係真真正正結構性影響，呢啲先係永久性令香港永不超生。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拖累香港經濟的從來不是磗頭同火堆，而是極權制度。</span></span><br />\n(如果作為全球三大金融體制之一嘅香港，係可以咁簡單就比磚頭同火堆拖垮，除咗話你無知之外我都冇嘢好講🤦🏻&zwj;♂️)<br />\n<br />\n#兄弟爬山<br />\n#撤回不能救香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">從777將焦點同仇恨轉移去警隊個刻開始，就再唔係撤回就可以了事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其餘四個訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n1. 不特赦被捕人士 = 佢可以繼續拉其他人，即係如果你曾經和平遊行之後，行多咗少少出去馬路， sorry，你可以等住警察拍門鎖人，非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n2. 不成立獨立調查委員會 = 正確化咗警察執法嘅姿態同標準，後果我都唔需要多講啦<br />\n<br />\n3. 不重啟落實雙普選進程討論 = 已經違反咗基本法，都唔使等到2047年。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個唔係以香港核心價值作為管理理念嘅人，冇得到香港人認受性嘅人，今次逃犯條例，下次仲有咩？</span></span>智慧燈塔？國歌法？辱警法？仲有千千萬萬千奇百趣嘅嘢等緊你<br />\n<br />\n4. 林鄭唔下台。呢個我冇乜所謂。反正落實左雙普選，佢都唔會存在。<br />\n<br />\n#四大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">破壞不是毀滅，唯有先破才能後立！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a9184738ee4b679b33b109694ef07df32f480f6","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"反淺黃左膠藍絲謬論"},{"pid":"4a9cdecc3e55852a5036607a815aef45e4d6e5b5","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:24:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff90346ac4b6e1538b5cb71ba22e16c08a287a1f","tid":1541053,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2080d2cbf924c7096668af9abd2e2a1f5a8a1510","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:25:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d2ad6ff6366c9862e3d1bf8bb68e9416e9ef46b","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"反謬論"},{"pid":"ee9198ab48b503ef87a9198968c5b06d09395541","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:25:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7718c14d3c03d6e45e194664d96e69ad7d09ee2","tid":1541053,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38789fbba42e0deb9f5420a22fab88fb02cc895f","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"017fef7d7a06e06d5d2d96a3ba7df3dfb0a33c37","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb0dedea8bdc72f1944cf9399e95f1bc48a1456f","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:51.000Z","msg":"撤你老母"},{"pid":"5b1eb3f72c0e102c32a33f066e4472d0dc1821c7","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:27:35.000Z","msg":"腦袋是很好的東西，一定要大家都有一個"},{"pid":"689f8222a045ec4e6b941de0a303b9a3455927e9","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ed4c8be14ff8f7dfffb343b631e1488d5402693b","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:27:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5ba5f393711681b425ecd51f75b0e6ff01fdde4b","tid":1541053,"uid":196604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a377fc19ce1e026681cdd596117a030b3a2c7b07","tid":1541053,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"[轉貼]<br />\n<br />\n近日，聽到好幾位淺黃朋友傾開，點解後生仔要搞破壞，而不每星期和平示威表達訴求<br />\n唔評論和平示威能否達到目的，因為各執一詞。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後生仔搞破壞會影響民生同香港永遠玩完？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n影響民生我同意，但要分清楚，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">激進示威活動只屬事件性，屬於短暫性/一次性</span></span>。外國咁多暴動(真係死人)，例泰國曼谷，法國巴黎等等，佢地經濟有冇受到永久性影響？好明顯完全冇！<br />\n做生意嘅人好明白呢d只係短暫性影響，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會影響社會結構同營商環境。</span></span><br />\n短時間社會經濟會受影響，但<s